      <h1 class='title'>NHS Recruitment</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c282WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_282ws' title='Col. 282WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c282WS' name='column_282ws' href='#column_282ws' rel='bookmark'>282WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06461'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_384'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-chris-grayling' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_384' title='Link to this speech by Mr Chris Grayling' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-chris-grayling" title="Mr Chris Grayling">Chris Grayling</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06461">To ask the Secretary of State for Health how many<span class="italic">(a)</span> administrators, <span class="italic">(b)</span> doctors and <span class="italic">(c)</span> nurses have been recruited by the NHS in the past 12 months. [88770]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06462'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_385'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-hutton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_385' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Hutton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-john-hutton" title="Mr John Hutton">Mr. Hutton</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06462">Information on the number of staff recruited to the national health service in the last 12 months is not separately available.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
